      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/cantor-fitzgerald-accuses-data-firm-of-extortion-in-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cantor Fitzgerald 起诉了托管其部分“最关键和最敏感数据”的公司，声称 IT Convergence Inc. 试图向其“勒索”钱财。]]></description>
